  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Welcome to Isle of the Night!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, you’ll gather resources, craft gear, and battle waves of enemies as you try to survive. By day, explore the island and prepare; by night, fight against powerful enemies. Whether you play solo or team up with friends, every choice matters in your fight for survival.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Craft, Build, Survive</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras/e8e91e4aa8939591f958c4a7b5e97916.poster.avif?t=1770238779\" width=800 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras/e8e91e4aa8939591f958c4a7b5e97916.webm?t=1770238779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras/e8e91e4aa8939591f958c4a7b5e97916.mp4?t=1770238779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather resources and craft essential tools and weapons. Build your arsenal by chopping trees, mining, and hunting for materials. Your survival depends on the gear you create.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Choose Your Own Build</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras/373c1788dc6343daaa2b507aa5b74227.poster.avif?t=1770238779\" width=800 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras/373c1788dc6343daaa2b507aa5b74227.webm?t=1770238779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras/373c1788dc6343daaa2b507aa5b74227.mp4?t=1770238779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from a variety of random upgrades and power-ups as you gain experience. Shape your playstyle with unique abilities and powerful boosts each time you level up.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dynamic Combat</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras/b768654b092d1ed1a80e75d442a0d302.poster.avif?t=1770238779\" width=800 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras/b768654b092d1ed1a80e75d442a0d302.webm?t=1770238779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras/b768654b092d1ed1a80e75d442a0d302.mp4?t=1770238779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine melee and ranged attacks, and unleash abilities tied to your gear for fast-paced, action-packed combat. And when you feel ready, challenge the powerful bosses that lurk under the island for the ultimate test of your skills.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Survive Together in Co-op</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras/abad64a89107608831e8c072f7df84d1.avif?t=1770238779\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras_big/abad64a89107608831e8c072f7df84d1.avif?t=1770238779 width=800 height=230 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up with friends. Share resources, strategize together, and gear up to face even tougher waves of enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Welcome to Isle of the Night!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, you’ll gather resources, craft gear, and battle waves of enemies as you try to survive. By day, explore the island and prepare; by night, fight against powerful enemies. Whether you play solo or team up with friends, every choice matters in your fight for survival.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Craft, Build, Survive</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras/e8e91e4aa8939591f958c4a7b5e97916.poster.avif?t=1770238779\" width=800 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras/e8e91e4aa8939591f958c4a7b5e97916.webm?t=1770238779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras/e8e91e4aa8939591f958c4a7b5e97916.mp4?t=1770238779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather resources and craft essential tools and weapons. Build your arsenal by chopping trees, mining, and hunting for materials. Your survival depends on the gear you create.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Choose Your Own Build</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras/373c1788dc6343daaa2b507aa5b74227.poster.avif?t=1770238779\" width=800 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras/373c1788dc6343daaa2b507aa5b74227.webm?t=1770238779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras/373c1788dc6343daaa2b507aa5b74227.mp4?t=1770238779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from a variety of random upgrades and power-ups as you gain experience. Shape your playstyle with unique abilities and powerful boosts each time you level up.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dynamic Combat</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras/b768654b092d1ed1a80e75d442a0d302.poster.avif?t=1770238779\" width=800 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras/b768654b092d1ed1a80e75d442a0d302.webm?t=1770238779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras/b768654b092d1ed1a80e75d442a0d302.mp4?t=1770238779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine melee and ranged attacks, and unleash abilities tied to your gear for fast-paced, action-packed combat. And when you feel ready, challenge the powerful bosses that lurk under the island for the ultimate test of your skills.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Survive Together in Co-op</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras/abad64a89107608831e8c072f7df84d1.avif?t=1770238779\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras_big/abad64a89107608831e8c072f7df84d1.avif?t=1770238779 width=800 height=230 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up with friends. Share resources, strategize together, and gear up to face even tougher waves of enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
